{"tid":2103031,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Elon Musk身家達705億美元超越巴菲特成世界第7大富豪","createTime":"2020-07-11T02:32:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T02:40:32.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a6cffbc6f1023c5709974ddb2f73c5d0dad64bae","tid":2103031,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T02:32:06.000Z","msg":"彭博億萬富翁指數（Bloomberg Billionaires Index）數據顯示，馬斯克週五財富增長61億美元，現為全球第7有錢的人，並擠下甲骨文創辦人埃利森（Larry Ellison）和谷歌共同創辦人之一的布林（Sergey Brin），布林排名本週稍早亦超越巴菲特。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克現約有705億美元財富，大部分是來自他持有約20%的特斯拉股票，而其太空公司SpaceX的多數股權約價值150億美元。此外今年稍早馬斯克的薪資也漲至5.95億美元，成為美國薪酬最高的執行長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3224942\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3224942&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=55a8394e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3224942&h=5eba5209\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3224942</a>"},{"pid":"f0d89ed964721edb5b2fd27aab8a35c0c38c2932","tid":2103031,"uid":134908,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T02:39:09.000Z","msg":"連燈仔：身家多過巴菲特條廢老有咩咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27f524264b39007e611dfe783779928884e9de